quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,105,"Is Quran ko humne haqq ke saath nazil kiya hai aur haqq hi ke saath yeh nazil hua hai. Aur (aey Muhammad) tumhein humne iske siwa aur kisi kaam ke liye nahin bheja ke (jo maan le usey) basharat de do aur (ja na maaney usey) mutanabbeh (warn) kardo"
  17,106,"Aur is Quran ko humne thoda thoda karke nazil kiya hai taa-ke tum thehar thehar kar isey logon ko sunao, aur isey humne ( mauqa mauqa se) ba-tadreej utara hai"
  17,107,"(Aey Muhammad), in logon se kehdo ke tum isey maano ya na maano, jin logon ko issey pehle ilm diya gaya hai unhein jab yeh sunaya jata hai to woh mooh ke bal sajde mein gir jatey hain"
  17,108,"Aur pukar uthte hain “paak hai hamara Rubb , uska wada to pura hona hi tha”"
  17,109,"Aur woh mooh ke bal rotey rotey huey gir jaate hain aur isey sunkar unka khushu (humility) aur badh jata hai"
  17,110,"(Aey Nabi), insey kaho, Allah kehkar pukaro ya rehman kehkar, jis naam se bhi pukaro uske liye sab acchey hi naam hain aur apni namaz na bahut zyada buland aawaz se padho aur na bahut past aawaz se, in dono ke darmiyan awsat darje ka lehja ikhtiyar karo"
  17,111,"Aur kaho “tareef hai us khuda ke liye jisne na kisi ko beta banaya, na koi baadshahi mein uska shareek hai, aur na woh aajiz (helpless) hai ke koi uska pushtbaan (supporter) ho” aur uski badayi bayan karo, kamaal darje ki badayi"
  18,1,"Tareef Allah ke liye hai jisne apne banday par yeh kitaab nazil ki aur ismein koi tedh na rakkhi"
  18,2,"Theek theek seedhi baat kehne wali kitaab, taa-ke woh logon ko khuda ke sakht azaab se khabardar karde, aur iman laa kar neik amal karne walon ko khush khabri de de ke unke liye accha ajar hai"
  18,3,"Jismein woh hamesha rahenge"
  18,4,"Aur un logon ko dara de jo kehte hain ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai"